Welcome to the W3C {{ group.name }}

The group meets in weekly teleconferences (currently Tuesday at 1600 UTC/11 Eastern).
Agendas are shared the day before. Connection information is available to group participants.

We use the mailing list public-web-adv@w3.org and the github repository 
https://github.com/w3c/web-advertising/#readme

See https://github.com/w3c/web-advertising/blob/main/BG-how-we-work.md 

Should you have any questions, please contact the W3C team contacts, copied on this introductory email.



